@startuml
title Flow Cautare Produs - TechStore

actor "Utilizator" as User
participant "SearchPage\n(React)" as SP
participant "productsApi.js" as API
participant "Express Server\n(Node.js)" as Server
participant "products.json" as JSON

User -> SP : Introduce numele produsului
User -> SP : Click Cauta
SP -> API : searchProduct(name)
API -> Server : GET /api/products/search?name=Widget
Server -> JSON : readFile
JSON --> Server : date produse
Server -> Server : filter by name

alt Produs gasit
    Server --> API : 200 OK
    API --> SP : results
    SP --> User : Afiseaza produs cu pret si cantitate
else Produs negasit
    Server --> API : 404 Not Found
    SP --> User : Mesaj eroare
    User -> SP : Click Da - adauga produs
    SP -> API : addProduct(name, price, quantity)
    API -> Server : POST /api/products
    Server -> JSON : writeFile
    Server --> API : 201 Created
    SP --> User : Produs adaugat cu succes!
end

@enduml